{"tid":1792852,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"bauhaus啲員工真係藍到仆街","createTime":"2019-12-22T03:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T21:30:36.000Z","uid":29969,"like":115,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8d57a2b8008981ebbd1a9c0b9741c8aca6bd9b0d","tid":1792852,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:21:53.000Z","msg":"話說我同朋友去左bauhaus返幾日開倉<br />\n吹吹下水講到啲政治問題<br />\n有個全職既過黎搭嗲話你有200萬人姐<br />\n我仲有500萬人係我果邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食飯果時佢會叫哂所有人外賣<br />\n跟住我地提議不如叫黃店比幾個選擇佢揀<br />\n佢又話唔喎 點解要分化 係都要叫藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人工又唔高 攰撚到仆街<br />\n啲老野全職又當啲兼職員工狗咁撚<br />\n少少尊重都唔識 真係痴撚線公司 898<br />\nBtw如果佢招聘請人 唔好見工入去<br />\n無謂主動去比啲藍絲老野撚"},{"pid":"a6e1f371b57a4cf4920edf6f0543d1804b87e8fd","tid":1792852,"uid":77092,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:24:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3eee2adbd49edfdb2ff5e77d0869cf9f5698d23e","tid":1792852,"uid":258683,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:24:19.000Z","msg":"500萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5f61c1bc4f81e403cf70630c199b5ea9e17ecb","tid":1792852,"uid":146285,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"有個全職既過黎搭嗲話你有200萬人姐，我仲有500萬人係我果邊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;&lt; 呢句都唔識駁番佢?"},{"pid":"c94ad49ec37afa3f09ee223cd0fee7b4ca07f363","tid":1792852,"uid":29969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:25:18.000Z","msg":"返左幾日就冇做<br />\n名都唔識叫<br />\n淨係叫人Number<br />\n當我係黑警定監躉呀"},{"pid":"f4cca2e3b077b76292c48b014ba0b6d872cc0bc8","tid":1792852,"uid":318369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T03:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q8j1mKZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ8j1mKZ.jpg&h=25794dd0&s